# Retromod Forge mod-file locator (#78): discovers jars in mods/Retromod/ so Retromod
# + transformed *-retromod.jar outputs can ship as CurseForge pack overrides instead
# of top-level mods/ jars. Read only by Forge (its ModDirTransformerDiscoverer scans
# mods/ for this service); ignored by Fabric and NeoForge, which use different SPIs.
com.retromod.locator.RetromodForgeModLocator
